Fukushima Water Decontamination System Resumes Operation

-- B y   Y u s u k e   M i y a z a w a
-- 
2011-08-07T09:15:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-07/fukushima-water-decontamination-system-resumes-operation.html
The water-decontamination system at
the Fukushima Dai-Ichi nuclear power plant resumed operation
after halting earlier today when a pump failed, a spokesman for
Tokyo Electric Power Co. who identified himself only by the
family name Kawamata said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yusuke Miyazawa in Tokyo at 
 ymiyazawa3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jim McDonald at 
 jmcdonald8@bloomberg.net  